{"word":"σφενδονάω","slug":"σφενδονάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σφενδονάω</b></el> <el>(σφενδονάω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to sling, to use the sling</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to strike by slinging</i>, <b><a href='S:Babrius'>Babr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to throw as from a sling</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to move like a swing, to swing to and fro</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:σφενδόνη'><el>σφενδόνη</el></a>\n"}]}